Package popt4jlib.PS.FA

Firefly Algorithm Parallel Implementation.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ChromosomeUpdaterIntf
    updates chromosome-i to move towards chromosome-j according to the params found in params.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DblArray1StdChromosomeUpdater
    the "standard" implementation of the position update for a firefly towards another, more "bright" one (see Wikipedia article: Firefly_Algorithm).
    DFA
    A parallel implementation of the Firefly Algorithm for function optimization, implementing also the SubjectIntf and ObserverIntf objects.
